world’s highest  shiva temple tungnath 📍

The same hump took the form of shiva-linga in Kedarnath. It is said that eventually, at four different locations four lingas emerged which represented four different parts of Lord Shiva's body. Tungnath represented the hands of Lord Shiva. Tunga in sanskrit means hands….🔱
